esign principles.\\n  - Effective communication and collaboration skills.\\n\\n• Areas for Improvement:\\n  - Explore opportunities to contribute to open-source projects.\\n  - Stay updated with the latest cloud services and technologies.\\n\\n----------------------------------------------------------\\n4. RECOMMENDATION\\n----------------------------------------------------------\\n\\nBased on the above evaluation, we recommend proceeding to:\\n  [X] Offer Extension\\n  [ ] Technical Lead Review\\n  [ ] Do Not Proceed\\n\\nRationale:\\n  Groot possesses the required technical skills, experience, and soft skills to excel in the Software Engineer position. His strong understanding of system design and cloud deployment makes him a valuable asset to the team.\\n\\n----------------------------------------------------------\\n5. NEXT STEPS & ACTION ITEMS\\n----------------------------------------------------------\\n\\n1. Extend an offer to Groot for the Software Engineer position.  \\n2. Schedule a follow-up meeting to discuss compensation and benefits.  \\n3. Onboard Groot to the team and provide necessary training resources.  \\n\\nReport generated by: Rocket Raccoon  \\nDate: August 7, 2024  \\n```\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": \"---\\n## VERSION 5\\n```text\\n1. Analyze the job description\\n2. Analyze the candidate resume\\n3. Conduct technical interview\\n4. Send emails as and when needed\\n5. Score candidate responses\\n6. Generate final evaluation report\\n```\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": \"---\\n## FEEDBACK to VERSION 5\\n```text\\n===============================\\nFINAL EVALUATION REPORT\\n===============================\\n\\nCandidate Name:       [Candidate Name]\\nCandidate Email:      [candidate.email@example.com]\\nPosition:             [Position Title]\\nInterview Date:       [Month DD, YYYY]\\nInterviewer:          [Interviewer Name], [Title]\\n\\n-----------------------------