cure interview folder.\\n2024-06-14 12:00 — Sent 'Interview Finished' email to candidate with timeline for feedback.\\n2024-06-15 09:30 — Saved raw interview data (recording, transcript, code files).\\n2024-06-15 10:00 — Scored each response against rubric:\\n   • Q1: Code correctness and efficiency (4/5).\\n   • Q2: System design depth and trade-offs (5/5).\\n   • Q3: Communication and teamwork examples (3.5/5).\\n2024-06-16 08:45 — Generated this final evaluation report.\\n\\nEnd of Report\\n------------------------------\\n```\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-27T18:17:57.260622\"\n}"}
